# ClientPortal / Application

## Commands

| Команда | Событие |
|---------|---------|
| `SubmitSiteLead` | `SiteLeadReceived` |
| `RegisterClient` | `ClientRegistered` |
| `UpdateClientProfile` | — |
| `SetClientPassword` | — |
| `SubmitReview` | `ReviewSubmitted` |
| `LinkGuestOrdersToClient` | `GuestOrdersLinkedToClient` |
| `ApproveReview` | `ReviewApproved` |
| `RejectReview` | `ReviewRejected` |

## Queries

`GetClientProfile`, `GetClientOrders` (флаг `history` вместо двух ES-queries), `GetClientOrderDetail`

Отдельного `GetOrderReview` нет — `review_exists` собирается через `ReviewRepository::findByOrderId` в controller/handler.

## Presenters

- `ClientOrderPresenter` — **без** статусов цеха (ADR-005); поля `review_exists` в list/detail
- `ClientProfilePresenter`, `ReviewPresenter`

## Support

`ClientLoader`

## Cross-BC

`SubmitReviewHandler`, `LinkGuestOrdersToClientHandler` → `OrderRepositoryInterface`

Handler инжектит repository ports, не Eloquent.
